Interface ResourceCore

  • All Known Subinterfaces:
    ImageCore, ImageCoreGray8, ImageThresholding
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    ImageCoreGray8IJ, ImageCoreIJ, ImageThresholdingIJ, ResourceCoreGeneric

    public interface ResourceCore
    GeneralInterface for resources such as images, videos, DNA sequence, signal, etc.
